data.description: Say hello to this AMAZING investment opportunity for a 3/2 in Stokesdale!! Discover Privacy and serenity on this sweet property. Fully fenced back, 2 year old roof, spacious rooms and closets! Large den w/ cozy fireplace. All this property needs is your vision and a some sweat to make it sparkly again. Easy access to I73, Oak Ridge, Summerfield, Greensboro, PTI Airport, anywhere in the Triad you want to be! Call today! Agents, see remarks.
